OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,FSwimmers have been told to avoid a
OL,7,Fhuge stretch of the Teesside coast
OL,8,Fafter untreated sewage was discharged
OL,9,Finto the water.
OL,11,FEmergency work is being carried out by
OL,12,FNorthumbrian Water after a main sewer
OL,13,Ffractured near Smith's Dock Road in
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough on Friday 26 June.
OL,16,FThe water company said it had
OL,17,Fdischarged diluted sewage from its
OL,18,Fstorm overflow in Redcar .
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
