CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1783698492
OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency has advised
OL,7,Fpeople not to swim at beaches around
OL,8,FSeaton Carew, Redcar, Marske and
OL,9,FSaltburn.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Environment
OL,12,FAgency said: "Following a discharge of
OL,13,Funtreated sewage after a main sewer
OL,14,Ffractured near Smith's Dock Road we
OL,15,Fhave had to issue temporary advice
OL,16,Fagainst bathing at designated bathing
OL,17,Fwaters in the Hartlepool and Redcar
OL,18,Fareas.
OL,26,@tD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1783698492
OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,F"Northumbrian Water are undertaking
OL,7,Frepair work and our teams are advising
OL,8,Fand monitoring the impacts from the
OL,9,Fdischarge.
OL,11,F"Our officers are undertaking
OL,12,Findependent sampling and inspections.
OL,13,FWe will not hesitate to take action if
OL,14,Fappropriate following an investigation
OL,15,Finto the incident."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1783698492
OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,FWarning signs have appeared near the
OL,7,Faffected beaches, which are Seaton
OL,8,FCarew North, Seaton Carew Centre,
OL,9,FSeaton Carew North Gare, Redcar
OL,10,FCoatham, Redcar Lifeboat Station,
OL,11,FRedcar Granville, Redcar Stray, Markse
OL,12,FSands and Saltburn.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Northumbrian Water
OL,15,Fsaid: "On Friday evening, (26th June)
OL,16,Fwe were made aware of a burst on our
OL,17,FCargo Fleet sewage main near Dockside
OL,18,FRoad in Middlesbrough.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1783698492
OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,F"Our teams attended quickly to assess
OL,7,Fthe damage and carry out
OL,8,Finvestigations.
OL,10,F"There is potential that this was
OL,11,Fcaused by a third party, but our teams
OL,12,Fare working around the clock to find a
OL,13,Fsolution and carry out repairs.
OL,15,F"Since then, they have been working
OL,16,Faround the clock to carry out repairs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1783698492
OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,F"Because of the damage to the main,
OL,7,Fsewage in the system has backed up,
OL,8,Fand we have needed to carry out very
OL,9,Fcontrolled, heavily diluted discharges
OL,10,Fthrough our storm overflow in Redcar.
OL,12,F"Our teams have been carrying out
OL,13,Fregular sampling and environmental
OL,14,Fmonitoring, and are also on-site
OL,15,Fcarrying out beach cleans.
OL,17,F"This is not a decision we have taken
OL,18,Flightly, but it is our only option to
OL,19,Fprotect customers from the devastation
OL,20,Fthat can be caused by internal sewage
OL,21,Fflooding.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1783698492
OL,3,C'Do not swim' advice issued after
OL,4,Csewage leak
OL,6,F"As a precaution, the Environment
OL,7,FAgency have advised against swimming
OL,8,Fin Redcar and Hartlepool beaches.
OL,10,F"Our teams will continue to work hard
OL,11,Fon site, and we are working closely
OL,12,Fwith the Environment Agency as well as
OL,13,Fthe local authorities and landowners,
OL,14,Fin order to resolve this as quickly as
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,17,F"We understand the frustration this
OL,18,Fwill cause and would like to thank
OL,19,Fcustomers for their patience."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
